<div class="text-center pt-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Get Involved with PermiePortal</h1>
  <p class="text-lg mb-6">
    Join our mission to promote permaculture principles, share knowledge, and foster a sustainable future. Here are some ways you can get involved:
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="text-left max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">🌱 Volunteer</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Help us grow our permaculture community by contributing your skills, time, and passion. From organizing events to managing our resources, there are plenty of ways to lend a hand!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-left max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">📚 Share Your Knowledge</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Submit articles, guides, or case studies on permaculture projects to expand our resource library. We welcome contributions from enthusiasts, practitioners, and experts alike.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-left max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">🤝 Join the Community</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Participate in discussions, attend workshops, and connect with like-minded individuals who share a passion for permaculture.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-8 text-lg">
    <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-800 border-b border-green-600">Sign up</a> to stay updated on the latest opportunities to get involved!
  </p>
</div>

